name: Simpleutil
body:
### Intro
This simple utility will help to perform common functions widely used by .NET developers, like converting DataTable to Excel or CSV. I tried to make it as generic as I could to ease the use.

### Who Need This
Anyone lazy enough to code those common codes.

### Authors and Contributors
Aditya Yedija Marojahan Situmeang (@yedijas)
